{"id": "30f76176-02c1-4483-9b1d-be051b69ec7d", "task_id": "07de7077-8f23-4b07-bf1b-6d12df59bf9c", "path": "templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Cyberpunk Login | Access Denied</title>\n    <!-- Link to the static CSS file provided by the FastAPI mount -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for('static', path='/css/style.css') }}\">\n    <!-- Cyberpunk font style -->\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"cyber-theme\">\n    <div class=\"scanlines\"></div>\n    \n    <div class=\"login-container\">\n        <div class=\"glitch-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"glitch\" data-text=\"NEURAL_LINK\">NEURAL_LINK</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"terminal-header\">\n            <span class=\"terminal-title\">TERMINAL_V.2.0.77</span>\n            <span class=\"status-indicator\">SYSTEM: <span class=\"status-online\">ONLINE</span></span>\n        </div>\n\n        <main class=\"login-box\">\n            <p class=\"prompt\">IDENT_REQUIRED // ENTER CREDENTIALS</p>\n\n            <!-- Jinja2 Error Placeholder -->\n            {% if error %}\n            <div class=\"error-container\">\n                <div class=\"error-header\">[ SECURITY ALERT ]</div>\n                <div class=\"error-body\">{{ error }}</div>\n            </div>\n            {% endif %}\n\n            <form action=\"/login\" method=\"POST\" class=\"cyber-form\">\n                <div class=\"input-wrapper\">\n                    <label for=\"username\">IDENTITY_CODE</label>\n                    <input \n                        type=\"text\" \n                        id=\"username\" \n                        name=\"username\" \n                        placeholder=\"USER_ID\" \n                        value=\"{{ username if username else '' }}\" \n                        required \n                        autocomplete=\"off\"\n                    >\n                    <div class=\"input-glow\"></div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"input-wrapper\">\n                    <label for=\"password\">CIPHER_KEY</label>\n                    <input \n                        type=\"password\" \n                        id=\"password\" \n                        name=\"password\" \n                        placeholder=\"\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\u2022\" \n                        required\n                    >\n                    <div class=\"input-glow\"></div>\n                </div>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"submit-btn\">\n                    <span class=\"btn-label\">INITIALIZE_SEQUENCE</span>\n                    <span class=\"btn-glitch-layer\"></span>\n                </button>\n            </form>\n        </main>\n\n        <footer class=\"login-footer\">\n            <div class=\"footer-deco-line\"></div>\n            <div class=\"footer-info\">\n                <span>ENCRYPTION: AES-256-GCM</span>\n                <span>ZONE: NIGHT_CITY_NET</span>\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // Subtle interactivity for the login button\n        const form = document.querySelector('form');\n        const btn = document.querySelector('.submit-btn');\n        \n        form.addEventListener('submit', () => {\n            btn.classList.add('processing');\n            btn.querySelector('.btn-label').innerText = 'CONNECTING...';\n        });\n\n        // Console log for flavor\n        console.log(\"%c [SYSTEM] Neural link handshake initialized...\", \"color: #00ff9f; font-weight: bold;\");\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "A high-fidelity cyberpunk login HTML structure using Jinja2 templates. It includes a dynamic error banner that triggers based on backend validation, input persistence for the username, and uses FastAPI's url_for for reliable static asset linking. The layout features decorative elements like scanlines and glitch containers to support the requested aesthetic.", "dependencies": ["https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap"]}, "created_at": "2026-05-17 13:42:28.676406"}